### Smartling Files API - List Files and Check Status
### Based on: https://api-reference.smartling.com/#tag/Files

# Your Smartling credentials
@project_id = 9233d2cb5
@user_identifier = YOUR_USER_IDENTIFIER
@user_secret = YOUR_USER_SECRET
@base_url = https://api.smartling.com
@auth_url = https://api.smartling.com/auth-api/v2/authenticate
@access_token = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

### 1. Authenticate to get access token (run this first)
POST {{auth_url}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userIdentifier": "{{user_identifier}}",
  "userSecret": "{{user_secret}}"
}

### 2. List all files in the project
GET {{base_url}}/files-api/v2/projects/{{project_id}}/files/list
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. List files with filters (optional parameters)
GET {{base_url}}/files-api/v2/projects/{{project_id}}/files/list?limit=100&offset=0&orderBy=fileUri&orderDirection=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Get file status for a specific file
GET {{base_url}}/files-api/v2/projects/{{project_id}}/file/status?fileUri=YOUR_FILE_URI
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Get file status with locale information
GET {{base_url}}/files-api/v2/projects/{{project_id}}/file/status?fileUri=YOUR_FILE_URI&includeAuthorizedLocales=true
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 6. Get detailed file information
GET {{base_url}}/files-api/v2/projects/{{project_id}}/file?fileUri=YOUR_FILE_URI
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 7. List files with specific file types
GET {{base_url}}/files-api/v2/projects/{{project_id}}/files/list?fileTypes=json,xml,properties
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 8. Get project locales
GET {{base_url}}/projects-api/v2/projects/{{project_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
